Great place for South Indian cuisine in Jackson Heights. This is a low key, no frills restaurant with some great vegetarian food. Love their thali, pav bhaji and idly-wada. Oh and the chaat is awesome too. Try their sev puri. It's tastes exactly like the one I used to have in Mumbai!
